data.meta_description: “The Australian Army is a highly respected National institution because of its people. It’s all about the people. If we communicate, and leverage off all in our organisation, not just our senior officers, our IQ will be awesome. Then there will be no job which is beyond us.” — Ken Gillespie quotes from QuoteFancy.com
